<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!--
    wear-bed-picker-onboarding D7: Spanish locale (`values-es`) for the
    bed-picker onboarding copy. The keys mirror the locked Spanish
    translations defined in §11.4 of design-files #425. The default
    English siblings live in `values/strings.xml`. This file is owned by
    PR-3b; PR-3c will add the three `home_*` / `action_*` keys (they
    must NOT be added here either until PR-3c).

    Clinical copy review (⚠ §12.1 carry-over): the strings in this
    file are tracked for Spanish clinical sign-off. Do NOT change them
    without clinical review.
-->
